title: The Game Keeps Evolving
description:
The NFL Live crew looks back on the exciting Monday Night Football game between the Washington Football Team and Seattle Seahawks; we analyze what the win means for Washington's playoff chances. Additionally, the crew will talk about how the game has evolved over time and which teams have pushed it forward!
